Name:           scdoc
Version:        1.11.1
Release:        0
Summary:        A man page generator written in C99
License:        MIT
Group:          Development/Tools/Doc Generators
URL:            https://git.sr.ht/~sircmpwn/scdoc/
Source:         https://git.sr.ht/~sircmpwn/scdoc/archive/%{version}.tar.gz
Source1:        scdoc-rpmlintrc
